Dependencies
============
* python-augeas
* python-sphinx


Modules
-------
* Mysql
  apt-get install python-mysqldb

Client
------
* python-prettytable
* pip install argcomplete

apt-get install python-augeas python-sphinx python-prettytable python-mysqldb


Test Lifecycle and Augeas
=========================
cd mss/agent/classes/mss3
export PYTHONPATH=$PWD
mkdir /tmp/etc
cp -r /etc/mysql /tmp/etc/


Non interactive test
---------------------
python tests/lifecycle.py

Interactive tests
-----------------
python agent-xmlrpc.py &
python client-xmlrpc.py help
python client-xmlrpc.py list
python client-xmlrpc.py load Mysql
python client-xmlrpc.py states Mysql
python client-xmlrpc.py goto Mysql Active -l     #list requires needed to go to Active
python client-xmlrpc.py goto Mysql Active port:8080 augeas_root:/tmp/
python client-xmlrpc.py provide Mysql


To get module documentation
---------------------------
python client-xmlrpc.py load Mysql
python client-xmlrpc.py dot Mysql > mysql.dot
dotty mysql.dot


To get full documentation
-------------------------
cd doc/
make html
firefox build/html/index.html


